  <title>O nome do ficheiro é demasiado largo</title>

  <p>Os documentos e as coleccións móstranse en forma de <gui>Reixa</gui> de maneira predeterminada. Para velos en forma de <gui>Lista</gui>:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press the list button in the top-right corner of the window.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <note style="info">
    <p>List view has columns displaying the document type and date modified,
    and whether it's stored locally or remotely in one of your online
    accounts.</p>
  </note>

  <p>Click the grid button in the top-right corner of the window to return to
  the grid view.</p>

